cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper deals with domain adaptation in deep neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural networks (cs.NE). However, since the paper focuses on deep neural networks and their application to image classification tasks, it is most likely to be classified under cs.LG and cs.CV.
